---
title: Zesty Garlic Chicken and Couscous Bowls with Tahini-Ranch Sauce
description: Equal parts savoury and zesty, this macro-conscious dinner is sure to wow you. Garlicky and juicy chicken breasts paired with a tangy DIY tahini-ranch sauce make this bowl irresistibly good.
